title: Steve Wilkos You Get Nothing
description:
YOU GET NOTHING

Where's my mother? 10-year-old Dillon wants one thing in his life more than anything, his mother Jessica. Unfortunately for Dillon, Jessica cares more for her drug addiction, than her own son. Jessica's mother Linda has been trying for years to get her daughter help, but at this point, she'd rather just raise Dillon herself. Will Steve get Jessica to break her addiction, or will drugs keep her from her life and her son forever?
